@startuml Sequence_Login
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam sequence {
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #EBF5FB
  ParticipantBorderColor #2980B9
  ArrowColor #2C3E50
  LifeLineBorderColor #BDC3C7
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #ECF0F1
  ActorBackgroundColor #FDEBD0
  ActorBorderColor #E67E22
}
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam NoteBorderColor #F9A825

title Sequence Diagram — Proses Login

actor "Pengguna" as User
participant "React Frontend" as FE
participant "AuthController" as AC
participant "User Model" as UM
participant "ActivityLog" as AL
database "Database" as DB

autonumber

User -> FE : Masukkan email & password\nlalu klik Login

FE -> FE : Validasi form (client-side)
note right: Cek email format\ndan password tidak kosong

FE -> AC : POST /api/login\n{ email, password }

AC -> AC : Validasi request\n(required|email + required)

alt Validasi gagal
  AC --> FE : 422 Unprocessable Entity\n{ errors }
  FE --> User : Tampilkan pesan error
end

AC -> DB : SELECT users WHERE email = ?
DB --> AC : User record

alt User tidak ditemukan
  AC --> FE : 422 { message: "Kredensial salah" }
  FE --> User : Tampilkan error
end

AC -> AC : Hash::check(password, user.password)

alt Password tidak cocok
  AC --> FE : 422 { message: "Kredensial salah" }
  FE --> User : Tampilkan error
end

AC -> UM : Cek is_active

alt Akun tidak aktif
  AC --> FE : 403 { message: "Akun tidak aktif" }
  FE --> User : Tampilkan error
end

AC -> DB : DELETE personal_access_tokens\nWHERE tokenable_id = user.id
note right: Hapus semua token lama

AC -> DB : INSERT personal_access_tokens\n{ name: "auth-token",\n  abilities: [role.slug] }
DB --> AC : Plain text token

AC -> DB : INSERT activity_logs\n{ user_id, action: "login",\n  resource: "Auth",\n  details: { ip } }

AC --> FE : 200 OK\n{ message, user: { id, name,\n  email, role, role_name }, token }

FE -> FE : Simpan token di localStorage\nSimpan user info di state

FE --> User : Redirect ke Dashboard
note right: Menampilkan halaman\nsesuai role pengguna

@enduml
